<hymn_number>445</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zài gē shēng lǐ huí dào jiā, zhǎo dào zì jǐ de duì wǔ, zài gē shēng lǐ huí dào jiā, zhǎo dào zì jǐ de xiōng dì,
 yī yàng de jiǎo yìn, liú gěi shān gāo shuǐ zhǎng, yī yàng de zhòng dān yī yàng de jīng lì
 kào zhǔ yé sū nǐ bāng wǒ, wǒ yě bāng zhù nǐ, rèn zuì huǐ gǎi qiān bēi shùn fú dù guò suì yuè de fēng yǔ,
 shǐ mìng shén shèng jiān zhēn, zhì sǐ bù yí, bù yào zài hū míng tiān qù dào nǎ lǐ.</lyrics>
<title>zài gē shēng lǐ huí dào jiā 迦南445</title>
</song>